<%- include('partials/head') %>
<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="wrap">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <h1>Careers at IndiaOffers 💼</h1>
    <p>We're a lean team of deal hunters — and our biggest opening isn't a desk job. It's you, hunting deals with us and getting rewarded for it.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="prose">
    <h2>Open position: Deal Hunter Partner 🎯</h2>
    <p><b>Work from anywhere. No fixed hours. No interviews.</b> If you're the friend everyone messages before a sale — the one who always knows where the loot is — this is for you.</p>
    <p>Become a part of IndiaOffers.in by <b>submitting deals you find directly on our site</b>. Every deal you submit is reviewed by our team; when it's approved, <b>you earn points that convert into real perks — free gifts, shopping vouchers and real money.</b> The better and hotter your deals, the more you earn.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="perk-grid">
    <div class="perk"><span class="pk-ico">🎁</span><h3>Free gifts</h3><p>Top hunters get surprise products shipped to their door — on us.</p></div>
    <div class="perk"><span class="pk-ico">💰</span><h3>Real money</h3><p>Convert your points into cash rewards and shopping vouchers.</p></div>
    <div class="perk"><span class="pk-ico">🏆</span><h3>Hunter status</h3><p>Climb the ranks — the best partners get early access and bonus point events.</p></div>
    <div class="perk"><span class="pk-ico">⏰</span><h3>Total freedom</h3><p>Submit one deal a month or ten a day. You choose your pace.</p></div>
  </div>

  <div class="prose">
    <h2>How it works</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><b>1.</b> <a href="/register" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:700">Create a free account</a> (takes under a minute).</li>
      <li><b>2.</b> Spot a great deal anywhere online — a price drop, a coupon stack, a loot.</li>
      <li><b>3.</b> Submit it via <a href="/submit-deal" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:700">Submit a Deal</a> with the link and price.</li>
      <li><b>4.</b> Our team verifies it. Approved deal = points in your account. Points = gifts, vouchers &amp; real money.</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-top:16px"><a class="btn-primary" href="/become-partner">See the full partner programme →</a></p>

    <h2>Other roles</h2>
    <p>We occasionally look for content writers (buying guides), coupon testers and social media hands. Drop us a line at <a href="mailto:<%= support.email %>" style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:700"><%= support.email %></a> with what you're great at — we read everything.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
